      "name": "Non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw, ASTM F1717 static loading only",
      "description": "Model applicability is restricted to non-cannulated titanium-alloy pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.5 mm and thread pitch 2.75 mm, tested under quasi-static ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration. Cannulated variants, dynamic fatigue loading, and screws outside the 6.5–8.5 mm diameter range are explicitly out of scope."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
