      "name": "ASTM F1717 quasi-static compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Valid operating range: axial compressive pre-load 0–600 N; bending moment arm fixed at 100 mm per ASTM F1717 fixture geometry; crosshead displacement rate 5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; relative humidity 30–70 %. Material property inputs bounded to Ti-6Al-4V ELI with E = 114 ± 3 GPa and σ_y = 880 ± 30 MPa."
    }
